title: Midlife Crisis LIT | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 46
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
The babes are back on the couch in studio and ready to serve up some TEA. This episode the babes just go full midlife crisis and have a big on air venting session. STRAP IN!
